{"tid":126222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"情變毆男友毀車　野蠻女友：佢強姦我！","createTime":"2017-02-19T07:46:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T08:23:25.000Z","uid":46231,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"538cbc67e14c39292cc2b81050ac8f27ab828f8e","tid":126222,"uid":46231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T07:46:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170219/bkn-20170219053526265-0219_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170219%2Fbkn-20170219053526265-0219_00822_001.html&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=ca9d29c5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170219/bkn-20170219053526265-0219_00822_001.html</a><br />\n旺角情困女涉毆男友毀車及報稱被強姦！昨深夜11時許，警方接獲報案，指海庭道1輛私家車上有人打架。警員到場在車上發現兩名男女，經初步調查，兩人因感情問題發生爭執，期間女子涉嫌毀壞車內倒後鏡；她又指早前在油麻地遭對方施暴。由於女事主手指受傷，其後送往醫院治理。 <br />\n<br />\n警方以涉嫌強姦將涉案姓何(42歲)男子拘捕；女事主(30歲)亦因涉嫌刑事毀壞及襲擊致造成實際身體傷害被捕，案件交由旺角警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n女人真係屈機  明明打爛人地架車<br />\n是但嗌句佢強姦我就可以搞鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1cc335c2bc267a3e37e20b8c8a0c0048e82f42","tid":126222,"uid":46231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T07:48:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4e4920a83c2ac171aac320b6091fdba636e1b7","tid":126222,"uid":14454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T07:48:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e901b5822cde7ff9b98dd43e9a2d22632b93652","tid":126222,"uid":32564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T07:51:17.000Z","msg":"勞資糾紛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c013f9e0969c02d35584a3dd71c999115229ab0","tid":126222,"